embeds.title: About ตัวอะไรไม่รู้
embeds.description:
ตัวอะไรไม่รู้ is a discord bot that is created by [CPE35 Developer](https://github.com/CPE35-Developer).
It is originally created for CPE35 KU81 Discord server.

You can also [invite ตัวอะไรไม่รู้ to your server](https://tinyurl.com/blackhole112) .

Feel free to checkout [ตัวอะไรไม่รู้'s GitHub repository](https://github.com/CPE35-Developer/discord-bot-aws).
